channel.title: Getting on Go Baby Go resource list
channel.description:
Hello all. I tried to email udgobabygo@udel.edu to get added to the Midwest resource list, and the email bounced. Any idea who I should contact to get added? Also, I was looking for a resource in the Chessapeake, VA area and there was not one listed. Anyone in this group in that area and could modify a jeep for a family?
Thanks!
